description:
In August we traditionally take a break from organising speakers, venues and food and skip to the one of my favourite parts of the meetup - Chatting and catching with members in the pub 🍹🍻 🍷

If you're interested in 🗣 http://cfp.swmobile.org/ at the Lighting talks meetup in September or another time please fill in our CFP form.

As has become a bit of a tradition, we'll be headed to The Volley.
title: SWmobile: summer social ☀
